---
title: Beef-Rosemary Meatballs and Onion Gravy with Smashed Potatoes and Sugar Snap Peas
description: In this meal, classic stew flavour gets condensed into a quick, 30-min recipe! Creamy mash cradles rosemary-studded meatballs doused in deeply savoury onion gravy. Crisp sweet peas bring it all together!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boulettes-de-boeuf-au-romarin-et-sauce-aux-oignons-2978c457.jpg
